Title: Commending Reverend Dr. Robert M. Waterman for special recognition after 18 years of serving as Pastor at the Antioch Baptist Church, Brooklyn, New York, to be celebrated on February 23, 2020
ActClause: LEGISLATIVE RESOLUTION commending Reverend Dr. Robert M. Waterman for special recognition after 18 years of serving as Pastor at the Antioch Baptist Church, Brooklyn, New York, celebrated on February 23, 2020
